Not Very Quick Quiz

Below are some teaser style questions.  They have been taken from "The  IQ
Challenge", a book written by 2 joint editors of the Mensa UK Puzzle Group
Journal,  Philip J Carter & Ken A Russell.  To enable you to monitor  your
performance throughout the quiz,  you will see a number of stars after the
question number. They are allocated as follows:

  	*  Standard
       **  More Challenging
      ***  Difficult
     ****  Appalingly Difficult


